data.description: 2.23 Acres of PEACE!!! Come see this beautiful SPACIOUS 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home with 2 separate living areas, tankless hot water heater, and a bonus room that is currently used as a bar! The utility room has room for your fridge, washer, and dryer! Come enjoy peace and solitude. Create the life you want. The property has a space for you to park your RV, a detached carport with storage, and 2 additional storage houses! Come create your own acre homestead!
